OL,3,CMan charged with murder after fatal
OL,4,Cassault in Pencoed
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man has been charged as
OL,7,Fpart of a murder investigation, after
OL,8,Fanother man was fatally assaulted
OL,9,Fbetween midnight and 5am on Saturday
OL,10,F28th February.
OL,12,FLiam Walters, 26, from Pencoed, has
OL,13,Fbeen charged with the murder of 58-
OL,14,Fyear-old David Rogers.
OL,16,FDavid Rogers died in hospital on
OL,17,FMonday, March 2, where he had been in
OL,18,Fa critical condition since being
OL,19,Fadmitted following the incident.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
