OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772708726
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after fatal
OL,4,Cassault in Pencoed
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the murder
OL,7,Fare continuing their appeal and anyone
OL,8,Fwho may have been in the vicinity of
OL,9,FFelindre Road, Pencoed between 12.30am
OL,10,Fand 4.30am on Saturday 28th February.
OL,12,FIn a previous statement Detective
OL,13,FInspector Graham Williams, from the
OL,14,FMajor Crime Investigation Team, said
OL,15,Fthe victim's family is being supported
OL,16,Fby specially trained officers.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
