OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1772708726
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after fatal
OL,4,Cassault in Pencoed
OL,6,F"I thank everyone in the community who
OL,7,Fhas helped our investigation so far,
OL,8,Fand I urge anyone with information
OL,9,Fwhich may be relevant, particularly
OL,10,Fthe two potential witnesses, to get in
OL,11,Ftouch."
OL,13,FAnyone with information should contact
OL,14,F101, quoting reference 2600063517.
OL,16,FLiam Walters will appears before
OL,17,FMagistrates Courts on Wednesday, 3rd
OL,18,FMarch.
